06:08.075 --> 06:11.271
You know what? You joke, Scott,
but what would you do, really?

06:12.840 --> 06:14.875
I don't understand.
Where did you guys find this place?

06:14.909 --> 06:17.277
"People" magazine said that
the Octomom used to eat here

06:17.311 --> 06:19.545
