the place I found.

06:33.058 --> 06:37.896
- John.
- You've gotta be kidding me.

06:37.930 --> 06:40.692
Turtle, can we be honest with you?

06:40.858 --> 06:43.267
- Please.
- Be honest with him, Gina.

06:43.301 --> 06:46.337
Hey, Turtle, we came to L.A. for
a free trip and to see some stars.

06:46.371 --> 06:48.366
