07:08.124 --> 07:09.725
- Well, that's--
- So do we like?

07:09.759 --> 07:11.931
- We love.
- What can you do on the price?

07:12.097 --> 07:14.096
You haven't even asked
what the price is yet.

07:14.130 --> 07:15.631
I'm sure I need it reduced.

07:15.665 --> 07:18.200
It's a great value and a great spot.

07:18.234 --> 07:21.036
No hard sell here,
but Wolfgang puck's people

07:21.070 --> 07:22.538
looked at it yesterday.

07:22.572 --> 07:24.540
I'm pretty sure they're
gonna make an offer.

07:24.574 --> 07:25.975
So if you don't want
to have a bidding war...

07:26.010 --> 07:27.911
We don't. We want it.
What do we gotta do?

07:27.945 --> 07:30.080
Sign the lease, give me
100k down payment.

07:30.114 --> 07:31.715
Turtle, you got your checkbook?

07:31.749 --> 07:33.117
- Uh...
- Write her a check, Turtle.

07:33.151 --> 07:36.087
Can you excuse us one second? Guys.

07:37.489 --> 07:39.924
Okay, I need you to tell me

07:39.958 --> 07:41.559
