07:41.593 --> 07:44.047
John is sentimental, Turtle,
and he believes in fate.

07:44.213 --> 07:46.397
- And?
- And when we woke up this morning

07:46.431 --> 07:48.265
and we were driving here,
we were talking about

07:48.300 --> 07:50.835
what a great place
this could be for our spot.

07:50.869 --> 07:52.404
Just then we saw it.

07:52.438 --> 07:55.741
And John looked up at the street name...
Bellarosa.

07:55.776 --> 07:59.912
- That's his mother's name.
- That's my mother's name, Turtle.

07:59.947 --> 08:01.380
She always loved Hollywood.

08:01.415 --> 08:04.683
So this is the place,
or there is no place.

08:09.822 --> 08:12.758
<i>♪ I live in a graveyard ♪</i>

08:15.528 --> 08:18.897
<i>♪ I wanna go out but it's too hot ♪</i>

08:21.434 --> 08:25.070
<i>♪ yeah, I'm just as see-through
as Casper the ghost... ♪</i>

08:25.105 --> 08:27.873
- Hi.
- Oh hi.

08:27.908 --> 08:30.076
I need to drop something
off for Sophia Lear.

08:30.110 --> 08:32.078
- I can take it.
- It's all right.

08:32.113 --> 08:33.613
I really need to speak to her.

08:33.648 --> 08:36.750
- Thanks.
- Um, let me see if she's in.

08:36.784 --> 08:38.308
- What's your name?
- Johnny Chase.

08:38.475 --> 08:40.655
- Hello, Johnny.
- <i>Sophia.</i>

08:40.688 --> 08:42.147
- How you doing?
- <i>I'm okay.</i>

08:42.313 --> 08:45.358
- What are you doing here?
- <i>I brought you something from Vince.</i>

08:45.393 --> 08:47.427
