10:06.063 --> 10:10.312
Moonves says he'll only make it
with Yagoda, however he wants.

10:10.346 --> 10:12.529
What does Yagoda say?

10:12.695 --> 10:14.549
He will not return my calls.

10:14.583 --> 10:19.487
Jake, get Phil Yagoda on the phone.

10:21.557 --> 10:23.057
Are you okay, Ari?

10:23.092 --> 10:26.461
This character, Lloyd...

10:28.031 --> 10:29.865
He loses his wife and his family,

10:29.899 --> 10:32.134
travels halfway across the
world to save these guys

10:32.169 --> 10:33.925
so they can be with
their loving families.

10:34.091 --> 10:36.506
- You know what the saddest part is?
- No.

10:40.444 --> 10:43.012
I don't even have my dog.

10:43.047 --> 10:46.082
This job, Vince...
It's all I got.

10:48.085 --> 10:49.482
Is your department ready?

10:49.648 --> 10:51.734
That's why I'm here.
They're waiting.

10:51.900 --> 10:54.090
All right, let's do this.

11:00.832 --> 11:03.399
I don't know most of you.
Why would I?

11:03.434 --> 11:05.101
I don't deal with TV.

11:05.135 --> 11:08.037
I especially don't deal
with made-for-TV movies.

11:08.072 --> 11:09.639
This is different.

11:09.673 --> 11:13.243
Vince Chase wants this
for his brother Johnny.

11:13.277 --> 11:16.679
Now we all know that Johnny
Chase may have limited talent,

11:16.714 --> 11:19.181
but like a child with special needs,

11:19.216 --> 11:21.472
