will stand by his side.

11:21.638 --> 11:24.620
<i>A real family member will buy
that child's way</i>

11:24.654 --> 11:27.255
<i>into Harvard if that's what it takes.</i>

11:27.290 --> 11:30.325
Vince Chase is standing
by his brother

11:30.360 --> 11:32.394
and I'm standing by both of them.

11:32.429 --> 11:36.399
Now I want every available
option on the table

11:36.433 --> 11:39.035
for how to get this film made
by the end of the day.

11:39.069 --> 11:42.673
Whoever succeeds will forever
be my family member.

11:42.707 --> 11:45.376
Whoever doesn't will be
cleaning tanning beds

11:45.410 --> 11:46.914
in fuckin' rancho cucamonga.

11:47.080 --> 11:49.292
I'm sorry, Ari.
Dana Gordon's on the phone for you.

11:49.458 --> 11:52.249
Looks like I just did
your job for you.

11:52.284 --> 11:54.318
You're all fired.

11:56.287 --> 11:58.722
She said a script that solid

11:58.757 --> 12:01.325
hasn't come across her desk
in a long time.

12:01.359 --> 12:05.183
I guess our boy Billy Walsh
has found his groove again.

12:05.349 --> 12:08.732
- I admit, it moved me.
- <i>Unfortunately,</i>

12:08.766 --> 12:11.334
she saw Zack Levi
from "Chuck" when she read it,

12:11.369 --> 12:14.237
- <i>not Drama.</i>
- That's not gonna work, Dana.

12:14.271 --> 12:15.805
<i>The script is an easy sell,</i>

12:15.839 --> 12:17.445
Drama is not.

12:17.611 --> 12:19.541
You know what? I'll call you back.

12:19.576 --> 12:21.610
<i>Are we having dinner tonight?</i>

12:21.644 --> 12:24.660
Listen, you jam it down hallmark's hall
of fame and we can have breakfast too.

12:24.826 --> 12:26.781
Goodbye, Ari.

12:26.816 --> 12:29.918
- Any word from Yagoda?
- No. They said he'd call back.

12:29.952 --> 12:31.753
Call Vince and tell him
I'll pick him up.

12:31.787 --> 12:33.920
We'll go to Yagoda's together.

12:34.086 --> 12:36.005
There's nothing shady
going on over here, Tex.

12:36.171 --> 12:40.510
Well, Turtle, when a guy tells you
he needs 250 grand and you say okay,

12:40.676 --> 12:42.998
<i>and then he says, "well, actually,</i>

12:43.032 --> 12:45.390
now I need 500 grand,"
it sounds shady.

12:45.556 --> 12:48.184
